sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant UIRoute as UI Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant UIProxy as UI OAuth Proxy<br/>TLS1.2+ JWT
    participant UI as ML Pipelines UI<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant APIRoute as API Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant APIProxy as API OAuth Proxy<br/>TLS1.2+ JWT
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant PersistenceAgent as Persistence Agent<br/>Service Account Token
    participant ScheduledWF as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Service Account Token
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP or 9000/TCP
    participant Tekton as Tekton API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PipelinePod as Pipeline Task Pods
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP via Envoy 9090/TCP

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Submit Pipeline via UI

    User->>Router: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    Router->>UIRoute: Forward to UI Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    UIRoute->>UIProxy: Reencrypt TLS<br/>OAuth Bearer Token
    UIProxy->>UI: HTTP<br/>3000/TCP (pod-local)
    UI->>APIServer: HTTP API Call<br/>8888/TCP Service Token
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Store Pipeline Definition<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    MariaDB-->>APIServer: Stored
    APIServer->>S3: Upload Artifacts<br/>Access/Secret Key
    S3-->>APIServer: Uploaded
    APIServer->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Service Token
    Tekton-->>APIServer: PipelineRun Created
    APIServer-->>UI: Pipeline Submitted
    UI-->>User: Confirmation

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    Tekton->>PipelinePod: Execute Tasks<br/>Various ports
    PipelinePod->>S3: Download/Upload Artifacts<br/>HTTPS TLS (if external)
    PipelinePod->>MLMD: Log Metadata<br/>9090/TCP gRPC (via Envoy)
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Store Metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Sync Pipeline Status

    PersistenceAgent->>Tekton: Watch PipelineRuns<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Service Token
    Tekton-->>PersistenceAgent: Status Update
    PersistenceAgent->>APIServer: Sync Metadata<br/>8888/TCP HTTP Service Token
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Update Run Status<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    ScheduledWF->>APIServer: Trigger Pipeline<br/>8888/TCP HTTP Service Token
    APIServer->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Service Token
    Tekton->>PipelinePod: Execute Tasks
    PipelinePod->>S3: Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/HTTP
    PersistenceAgent->>MariaDB: Update Status<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
